<msbt attribsize="4">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，晚上好！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚的星空真是美丽呢！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晚上好，<tag a="110" b="1" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />您看过夜空了吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />颗颗流星正从夜空中划过呢！
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让我们一同欣赏<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这绚丽的天文表演吧！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了对了！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我又在书里发现了有关星星的手册，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />上面还记了重要的笔记！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就把它给您了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />您愿意的话可以做做看！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，让我们彼此<delay20 />
度过一个美好的夜晚吧！</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="010_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />先使用<colour id="1" />摇杆<colour id="65535" />仰望星空的时候，<delay20 />
如果发现有流星划过，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这时按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />，<delay20 />
就可以完成许愿啦！<delay frames="30" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />要是能在流星消失前<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />许下愿望的话，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也许会有好事发生哦！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="010_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道您有没有发现，<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上看到的流星，<delay8 />
经常在短时间内接连划过？！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到一颗流星后，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也许应该保持仰望天空的姿势，
等待<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下一颗流星的出现呢！</message>
	<message label="010_03" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="1" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />您知道星座<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />各有各的故事吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果您给我看了与星座有关的物品，<delay20 />
我或许会为您讲述<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我所知道的<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />星座的故事。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有很多话我身为理科生很难理解，<delay20 />
不知道是什么意思。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我没信心能把故事讲好<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="02 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 />您有什么事吗？</message>
	<message label="011_a" attrib="00 00 00 00">请看看这个！</message>
	<message label="011_b" attrib="00 00 00 00">我们来说说话吧</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay8 />
没错呢！</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，让我们彼此<delay20 />
度过一个美好的夜晚吧！</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了对了！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前有一天晚上，<delay8 />
星光比平时更美，然后第二天早上，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我便捡到了这样的东西。
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为真的非常漂亮，<delay20 />
所以我想把这份好运<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也分给<tag a="110" b="1" />一点！</message>
	<message label="051" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />关于摩羯座的故事<delay8 />
有很多种版本，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一个是这样的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />某日在尼罗河边，<delay8 />
诸神正享受着酒宴，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />妖魔之父提丰突然出现。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />受到惊吓的诸神<delay8 />纷纷化身动物仓皇而逃，<delay20 />
牧神潘恩原本打算变身山羊跃入河中，<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但慌乱之间下半身却成了鱼尾。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />宙斯看到他半鱼半羊的样子觉得非常滑稽，<delay8 />
于是把这个形象幻化成了星座，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />并命名它为摩羯座。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我不太懂这个故事在说什么，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但变身失误的造型被化成星座，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />潘恩<delay8 />好可怜啊<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="052" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />关于水瓶座的故事<delay8 />
有很多种版本，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一个是这样的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />从前，奥林匹斯宫殿中<delay20 />有位名叫赫柏的少女，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />她担任着为众神斟酒的职务。<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过在她结婚之后，这个职位便空缺了。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />赫柏的父亲宙斯<delay8 />化身成一只鹰，<delay8 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />强行带回一人要其担任斟酒官，<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那人便是超级美少年甘尼美提斯！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />在宴席上侍奉诸神是一件很光彩的事，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />宙斯为了让甘尼美提斯的父母也能看到，<delay20 />
于是将他拿着水瓶的身姿幻化成了星座。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我不太懂这个故事在说什么，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay8 />突然莫名其妙被带走，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />长得帅也挺不容易的<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="053" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />关于双鱼座的故事<delay8 />
有很多种版本，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一个是这样的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />某日在尼罗河边，<delay8 />
诸神正享受着酒宴，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />妖魔之父提丰突然出现。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />众神仓惶向河中逃去，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />阿芙洛狄忒为防止与儿子厄洛斯走散，<delay8 />
就用绳子将自己与厄洛斯绑在了一起。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />随后他们化身成鱼逃走，<delay20 />
被绳索绑住的两条鱼的形象<delay8 />
便成了日后的双鱼座。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我不太懂这个故事在说什么，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但阿芙洛狄忒是爱与美的女神，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我更希望她以原本的样子化身成星座呢。</message>
	<message label="054" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />关于白羊座的故事<delay8 />
有很多种版本，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一个是这样的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />某位国王与王妃<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />育有一对双胞胎兄妹，<delay8 />
分别取名为佛里克索斯和赫勒。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />后来<delay8 />国王与王妃离婚了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />新王妃总是虐待这对兄妹，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把两人视作眼中钉。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为新王妃的阴谋，<delay20 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />兄妹两人的生命<delay8 />受到了威胁。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />两人的生母<delay8 />向宙斯求救，<delay20 />
从天而降的金毛羊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在千钧一发之际救出这对兄妹，<delay8 />向高空飞去。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这只金毛羊便是白羊座的原型。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我不太懂这个故事在说什么，<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过我发现，<delay20 /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />众神之王宙斯<delay8 />
经常出现在星座的故事里呢！</message>
	<message label="055" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />关于金牛座的故事<delay8 />
有很多种版本，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一个是这样的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在某个国度，<delay8 />有位名叫欧罗巴的公主，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />她长得十分美丽动人。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一天欧罗巴和她的女伴们<delay8 />
一同来到海边的牧场采摘鲜花时，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一头白色的公牛出现在她们面前。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就在欧罗巴骑上这头<delay8 />
十分温顺的公牛时，<delay20 /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />公牛载着她
突然向海面奔去，越跑越远直至消失。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实，这头牛的真身是众神之王宙斯。<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因倾心于欧罗巴的美貌，希望娶其为妻，<delay20 />
所以强硬地将她带走了。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当时宙斯化身的那头牛便是金牛座的原型。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它带着欧罗巴去到的大陆，<delay8 />
便是如今的欧洲。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我不太懂这个故事在说什么，<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我觉得万神之王宙斯<delay frames="30" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
这么做好像有点太过分了<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="056" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />关于双子座的故事<delay8 />
有很多种版本，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一个是这样的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很久以前，<delay8 />众神之王宙斯的儿子中<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有卡斯托耳<delay8 />和波吕克斯<delay8 />
这样一对非常英勇的兄弟。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他俩的感情非常深厚，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但只有波吕克斯继承了宙斯的血统，<delay20 />
拥有不死之身。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一次战争时，<delay8 />卡斯托耳不幸战死沙场，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />万分悲伤的波吕克斯放弃不死之身，<delay20 />
与兄弟一起升上夜空化作了双子座。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我不太懂这个故事在说什么，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我从中感受到的兄弟之情<delay8 />很令人感动。<10_4 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />完全想象不出是宙斯儿子的作风呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="057" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />关于巨蟹座的故事<delay8 />
有很多种版本，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一个是这样的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一次，<delay8 />怪物许德拉向泉水里投毒，
给当地百姓的生活造成了极大的困扰。<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />赫拉克勒斯听说后<delay20 />便前去击退许德拉。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一番苦战后，<delay8 />正当许德拉要遭受最后一击时，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一只很大的蟹跑出来想要帮助许德拉，<delay20 />
却被赫拉克勒斯轻而易举地踩死了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />宙斯的妻子赫拉<delay8 />觉得这只蟹很可怜，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />便将它幻化成了巨蟹座。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我不太懂这个故事在说什么，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但愿意在危急时刻出手相救真的很厉害，<10_4 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算是坏人的朋友<delay8 />也令人敬佩<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="058" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />关于狮子座的故事<delay8 />
有很多种版本，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一个是这样的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在希腊的墨涅亚大森林里，<delay8 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />住着一头吃人的大狮子，<delay20 />
赫拉克勒斯打算前去击退它。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />弓箭、棍棒、宝剑，这些都无法伤到狮子，<delay20 />
最后他徒手勒住狮子的脖子<delay8 />三天三夜，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才终于将狮子击败。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />众神之王宙斯的妻子赫拉<delay20 />
觉得与赫拉克勒斯激战的狮子<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />相当勇猛，<delay20 />
便将它幻化成了星座。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我不太懂这个故事在说什么，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我觉得，<delay8 />赫拉她呀，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是很讨厌赫拉克勒斯呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="059" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />关于处女座的故事<delay8 />
有很多种版本，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一个是这样的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />宙斯和德墨忒尔的女儿<delay8 />珀耳塞福涅<delay20 />
有一天外出采花的时候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />被冥王哈迪斯掳到了冥府。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />得知此事后的丰饶女神<delay20 />
德墨忒尔悲伤欲绝，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大地上的作物不再生长。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />万神之王宙斯看到了众生疾苦，<delay8 />
便去说服冥王哈迪斯归还珀耳塞福涅，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />母女二人终于得以团聚。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />处女座手持稻穗的形象，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />据说就是以母亲德墨忒尔为原型的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我不太懂这个故事在说什么，<delay20 />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过我知道了处女座的原型不是女儿是母亲。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话又说回来，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />被掳走的是宙斯的亲生女儿，
他为什么不早一点出面呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="060" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />关于天秤座的故事<delay8 />
有很多种版本，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一个是这样的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正义女神忒弥斯拥有一架神奇的天秤，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以用来评判人的善恶，<delay8 />
并将恶人贬去冥界。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />据说，<delay8 />
在潘多拉打开魔盒之前，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这架天秤几乎无用武之地。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这架神奇的天秤，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像就是天秤座的原型了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不太明白这个故事在说什么，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原来人的善恶也是可以称出分量来的啊<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="061" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />关于天蝎座的故事<delay8 />
有很多种版本，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中一个是这样的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />俄里翁是一位非常有能力的渔夫，<delay20 />
也因此平日里总是非常<delay8 />骄傲自大。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样毫不谦虚的态度惹怒了众神，<delay8 />
他们放出一只拥有剧毒的蝎子将他刺伤，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />俄里翁就这样被毒死了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />时至今日俄里翁都惧怕着蝎子，<delay20 />
